author: maxb
msg: Merge r10324 from trunk to 1.1.x branch.
Fix a simple bug when avoiding setting time stamps on special
files.  This can cause svn to abort when checking out/updating a
symlink pointing to a non-existant path.

author: maxb
msg: Merge r10317 from trunk to 1.1.x branch.
URIs never should end in a / when returned from svn_path_canonicalize().
Justification: http://svn/ would result in an assertion failure. Very ugly.

author: maxb
msg: Merge r10313 from trunk to 1.1.x branch.
Shouldn't tell people that --without-berkeley-db will keep us
from building the server parts of Subversion when it really doesn't.
